text: Canellakis, Kanellakis, Κανελλάκης is a Greek surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Karina Canellakis (born 1981), American conductor and violinist *Nicholas Canellakis (born 1984), American cellist *Paris Kanellakis (1953 – 1995), Greek American computer scientist Category:Greek-language surnames
